size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, June 10, 2025 8:50 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-06-10 8:50 a.m.", "text": "", "content_html": "", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": "<div class=chatlog__forwarded><div class=chatlog__forwarded-header><svg class=chatlog__forwarded-icon><use href=#forward-icon></use></svg> <em>Forwarded</em></div><div class=\"chatlog__forwarded-content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"caelkash_10391\">@Random Citizen</span> Spoke too soon. Been out and away from T1000e. Have come back, connected and it&#39;s been deaf for 3 hours. Won&#39;t receive messages.</span></div><div class=chatlog__forwarded-timestamp><span title=\"Tuesday, June 10, 2025 8:48 a.m.\">Originally sent: 2025-06-10 8:48 a.m.</span> <span title=\"Tuesday, June 10, 2025 8:49 a.m.\"> (edited)</span></div></div>"}, {"id": "1382017170279633027", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, June 10, 2025 11:22 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-06-10 11:22 a.m.", "text": "indeed weird. have any other node to test traces with?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>indeed weird. have any other node to test traces with?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1382091293282533506", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, June 10, 2025 4:17 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-06-10 4:17 p.m.", "text": "can you compile t1000 with all the debug flags?", "content