mestamp_short": "2025-08-16 4:21 p.m.", "text": "@VP was that generated by LLM?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"codeventz\">@VP</span> was that generated by LLM?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1406373059283128331", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 16, 2025 4:24 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-16 4:24 p.m.", "text": "src/helpers/nrf52/SerialBLEInterface.* is used in all nrf52 devices.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">src/helpers/nrf52/SerialBLEInterface.*</code> is used in all nrf52 devices.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1406373515468345447", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 16, 2025 4:26 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-16 4:26 p.m.", "text": "some of the \"identified issues\" seems to be over the board imho. needs more understanding, tuning and testing", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>some of the &quot;identified issues&quot; seems to be over the board imho. needs more understanding, tuning and testing</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1406373897196273665", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 16, 2025 4:27 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-16 4:27 p.m.", "text": "that's why I don't use LLMs on the MeshCore firmware source.. sometimes LLMs create very strange/bad decisions. especially chatgpt, which can't absorb whole codebase to understand what's happening under the hood", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>that&#39;s why I don&#39;t use LLMs on the MeshCore firmware source.. sometimes LLMs create very strange/bad decisions. especially chatgpt, which can&#39;t absorb whole codebase to understand what&#39;s happening under the hood</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}]}